<topic id="preferences-mark-occurrences">
  <title>Mark Occurrences Preferences</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Preferences<indexterm>Mark Occurrences</indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_unp_bgk_54b">This preferences page specifies which types of files will have the <xref
        href="highlight-xml-id-idrefs.dita#highlight-xml-id-idrefs" format="dita"
        product="developer editor developerEclipse editorEclipse">Highlight IDs
        Occurrences</xref><ph product="json">Highlight IDs Occurrences</ph> feature activated. To
      configure these options, <ph conkeyref="reusables-preferences-pages/open-the-preferences-page"
      /> and go to <menucascade>
        <uicontrol>Editor</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Mark Occurrences</uicontrol>
      </menucascade>:</p>
    <p id="p_vnp_bgk_54b">The following options are available in this preferences page:</p>
    <p id="p_wnp_bgk_54b">
      <dl id="dl_xnp_bgk_54b">
        <dlentry id="dlentry_ynp_bgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol>Highlight component occurrences in the current file for</uicontrol>:</dt>
          <dd>
            <ul id="ul_f66964dd-aca0-4939-8563-32fc4d17017f">
              <li id="li_znp_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><uicontrol>XML files</uicontrol> - Activates the <xref
                  href="highlight-xml-id-idrefs.dita#highlight-xml-id-idrefs" format="dita"
                  product="developer editor developerEclipse editorEclipse">Highlight IDs
                  Occurrences</xref><ph product="json">Highlight IDs Occurrences</ph> feature in XML
                files.</li>
              <li id="li_a4p_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><uicontrol>XSLT files</uicontrol> - Activates the <xref
                  href="schematron-highlight-component-occurrences.dita#schematron-highlight-component-occurrences"
                  format="dita" product="developer editor developerEclipse editorEclipse">Highlight
                  Component Occurrences</xref><ph product="json">Highlight IDs Occurrences</ph>
                feature in XSLT files.</li>
              <li id="li_b4p_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><uicontrol>XML Schema files</uicontrol> - Activates the <xref
                  href="schematron-highlight-component-occurrences.dita#schematron-highlight-component-occurrences"
                  format="dita" product="developer editor developerEclipse editorEclipse">Highlight
                  Component Occurrences</xref><ph product="json">Highlight IDs Occurrences</ph>
                feature in XSD files.</li>
              <li id="li_c4p_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><uicontrol>WSDL files</uicontrol> - Activates the <xref
                  href="schematron-highlight-component-occurrences.dita#schematron-highlight-component-occurrences"
                  format="dita" product="developer editor developerEclipse editorEclipse">Highlight
                  Component Occurrences</xref><ph product="json">Highlight IDs Occurrences</ph>
                feature in WSDL files.</li>
              <li id="li_d4p_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><uicontrol>RNG files</uicontrol> - Activates the highlight component occurrences
                feature in RNG files.</li>
              <li id="li_e4p_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><uicontrol>Schematron files</uicontrol> - Activates the <xref
                  href="schematron-highlight-component-occurrences.dita#schematron-highlight-component-occurrences"
                  format="dita" product="developer editor developerEclipse editorEclipse">Highlight
                  Component Occurrences</xref><ph product="json">Highlight IDs Occurrences</ph>
                feature in Schematron files.</li>
              <li id="li_f4p_bgk_54b" product="developer editor json" irina="irina"><uicontrol>Ant
                  files</uicontrol> - Activates the <xref
                  href="highlight-component-occurencies-ant.dita#highlight-component-occurencies-ant"
                  format="dita" product="developer editor">Highlight Component Occurrences</xref><ph
                  product="json">Highlight IDs Occurrences</ph> feature in Ant files.</li>
            </ul>
          </dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry product="developer editor json" id="dlentry_g4p_bgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol>Declaration highlight color</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Allows you to choose the color to be used for highlighting component
            declarations.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry product="developer editor json" id="dlentry_h4p_bgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol>Reference highlight color</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Allows you to choose the color to be used for highlighting component references.</dd>
        </dlentry>
      </dl>
    </p>
  </body>
</topic>
